# CellBender -------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Ref: 
https://cellbender.readthedocs.io/en/latest/index.html

Usage:
cellbender remove-background --cuda --input input_file.h5 --output output_file.h5

Note:
Pre-requisites:
raw_feature_bc_matrix.h5: A raw h5 count matrix file produced by cellranger count. (In CellRanger v2 this file was called raw_gene_bc_matrices_h5.h5).

